Class ConstL12Normalizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.ReferenceCountingBase

        • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.L12Normalizer
          • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.ConstL12Normalizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SampledTrainable, Trainable, TrainableDataMask, ReferenceCounting

    public class ConstL12Normalizer
extends L12Normalizer
implements SampledTrainable, TrainableDataMask
    This Trainable wrapper adds additional L1 and L2 terms for weight normalization. Both coefficients are universal for the network (does not depend on layer) and are setByCoord statically.
